data.eml:eml: Two new species of Parandrinae (Coleoptera: Cerambycidae) in the genera Parandra and Acutandra from South America

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Lingafelter, Steven W., Tishechkin, Alexey K. (2017): Two new species of Parandrinae (Coleoptera: Cerambycidae) in the genera Parandra and Acutandra from South America. Zootaxa 4272 (3): 401-410, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4272.3.5
